*Precision Scanning for Faster Order Processing.*




Say goodbye to the "Type-and-Typer" era. We=E2=80=99ve just supercharged th=
e item
reduction flow for our riders!

We=E2=80=99ve added a *Barcode Scan* feature to the "Update Items" screen. =
Instead
of manually typing long SKU numbers to find an item that needs to be
adjusted, riders can now simply tap the scan icon to instantly filter the
list.


What=E2=80=99s New

   -

   *Search gets a Sidekick:* Look for the new *Scanner Icon* in your search
   bar.
   -

   *Scan & Go:* Tap the icon, scan the barcode, and the app will instantly
   pull up the exact product for you.
   -

   *Precision Picking:* By matching the scan directly to the SKU, we=E2=80=
=99ve
   killed manual errors for good.


[image: image placeholder]


Why it matters?


This feature is built to make your operations smoother and your decisions
sharper:

   -

   *Error Reduction:* Eliminates manual entry mistakes


   -

   *Speed:* Reduces item lookup time by up to 70%.


   -

   *Accuracy:* Ensures the rider is adjusting the exact SKU intended by
   matching the scan output directly against the product array.



That's It!


Update now and feel the speed!=E2=9A=A1=EF=B8=8F
